<TEXT PARTNO="003">
We should understand that <COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">the government</COREF> is no panacea for all ills .
The driving force for economic development and societal progress is the people .
Over the past half - century , the Taiwanese people have toiled hard to create an economic miracle that has won global applause , and to lay the foundation for the survival and development of <COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">the Republic of China</COREF> .
