In the future , <COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">the government</COREF> should not necessarily play the role of a " leader " or " manager . "
On the contrary , <COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> should be the " supporter " and " service provider , " as expected by private enterprises .
