<COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">The government</COREF> will find <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">solutions for issues relating to the people 's lives , such as law and order , social welfare , environmental protection , land - use planning , waste disposal , river cleaning , transportation and community renewal</COREF> .
